<p>The EAA is introducing a staged registration model to identify accountable operators and, where applicable, individual unmanned aircraft used in regulated activities.</p>
<h2>How registration is expected to work</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Operator account creation with contact and accountability details.</li>
  <li>Aircraft declaration including class, mass range and intended operation type.</li>
  <li>Issue of operator identifier for display where required.</li>
</ul>
<h2>What the future register will do</h2>
<p>The future service will provide secure account management, renewal reminders and status confirmation for compliance checks.</p>
<div class="callout"><strong>Coming soon:</strong> Endonian UAS online registration service. Public launch window currently targeted for Q1 next year.</div>
